<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Maryam | Portfolio</title>
<style>
body{margin:0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:2vh;}
h1{font-size:3vh;font-weight:700;margin:1vh 0;}
p{font-size:2vh;margin:1vh 0;}
.card{background:#2d2d2d;border:0.4vh solid #ff4da6;border-radius:2vh;padding:2vh;margin:2vh auto;max-width:90%;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(255,77,166,0.25);transition:transform 0.2s ease,box-shadow 0.2s ease;}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(255,77,166,0.35);}
img{width:15vh;height:15vh;border-radius:50%;border:0.4vh solid #ff4da6;}
.themebtn{background:#ff4da6;border:none;color:#fff;padding:1vh 2vh;border-radius:1vh;font-size:2vh;cursor:pointer;margin-top:1vh;}
body.light{background:#f5f5f5;color:#111;}
body.light .card{background:#fff;border-color:#ff1493;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(255,20,147,0.15);}
body.light .themebtn{background:#ff1493;border:2px solid #d63384;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
<img src="https://i.ibb.co/placeholder/yourphoto.jpg" alt="Maryam">
<h1>Hi, I’m Maryam 👑</h1>
<p>Frontend developer learning HTML, CSS, JS</p>
<button class="themebtn" onclick="document.body.classList.toggle('light')">Toggle Mode</button>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Projects</h2>
<p>Day 1 - My first page</p>
<p>Day 2 - Portfolio with dark mode</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
